summary: So I hate Michael Sheen with all my heart.    No I don’t I think he’s absolutely adorable and I am definitely at that point in...
body:
So I hate Michael Sheen with all my heart. 

  No I don’t I think he’s absolutely adorable and I am definitely at that point in my life where I’m going to be stupid and hunt down everything he’s ever acted in   

I’m watching Masters of Sex and I want to slap this stupid man so hard.  It’s not supposed to be funny but his completely disaffected face while he watches everyone else having sex in front of him is hilarious.  I’m also a fan of how inconsistent his accent gets during emotional scenes.
